lighting soft
material dull
graphics silhouettes true width 1.5
view #1/X:26,31,40,41,44
zoom 0.55
save overlay_check.png width 1400 height 1050 supersample 2
hide #3 models
save overlay_new_solo.png width 1400 height 1050 supersample 2
exit